VALUES
(52, 1, 1, 45, 1, 7, 7, 'Grace be unto you, and peace', 'Grace and Peace Greeting', 'Both passages emphasize the greeting of grace and peace from God the Father and the Lord Jesus Christ. This connection highlights a common theme in Paul''s letters, establishing a sense of unity and blessing among believers.', 'theme', 0.384, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 1, 53, 1, 1, 1, 'the church of the Thessalonians', 'Connection Between Thessalonian Letters', 'Both passages emphasize the same greeting structure and the unity of the church in God and Christ. The consistent mention of Paul, Silvanus, and Timotheus further reinforces their shared authorship and message.', 'parallel', 0.349, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 1, 44, 18, 5, 5, 'Silvanus, and Timotheus', 'Connection Between Paul and Companions', 'Both passages emphasize the presence of Silas and Timothy alongside Paul. Their collaboration in ministry is evident, linking their roles in the church of the Thessalonians and their journey in Macedonia.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 1, 44, 20, 4, 4, 'the church of the Thessalonians', 'Connection of Thessalonian Believers', 'Both passages emphasize the presence of Thessalonians in early Christian communities. In 1 Thessalonians, Paul addresses the church of the Thessalonians, while Acts mentions Thessalonian individuals accompanying Paul.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 1, 47, 1, 19, 19, 'Silvanus, and Timotheus', 'Connection of Paul and Associates', 'Both passages emphasize the involvement of Paul, Silvanus, and Timotheus in preaching to the churches. This connection highlights their collaborative ministry and the unity in their message about Jesus Christ.', 'parallel', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 1, 49, 1, 2, 2, 'Grace be unto you, and peace', 'Grace and Peace Greeting', 'Both passages emphasize the greeting of grace and peace from God the Father and the Lord Jesus Christ. This connection highlights a common theme in Pauline letters, establishing a tone of blessing and unity.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 1, 51, 1, 1, 1, NULL, 'Shared Authorship and Greeting', 'Both passages emphasize the presence of Paul and Timotheus as authors, highlighting their collaborative role in addressing the churches. This connection illustrates a common practice in early Christian letters of including co-authors.', 'parallel', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 2, 45, 1, 8, 9, 'making mention of you in our prayers', 'Expressions of Gratitude in Prayer', 'Both passages emphasize giving thanks to God and making mention of others in prayers. This connection highlights the importance of prayer and gratitude in the early Christian community.', 'theme', 0.391, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 2, 49, 1, 15, 16, 'making mention of you in our prayers', 'Expressions of Gratitude in Prayer', 'Both passages emphasize giving thanks to God and making mention of the recipients in prayers. This connection highlights a shared theme of gratitude and intercession for fellow believers.', 'theme', 0.377, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 2, 57, 1, 4, 4, 'making mention of you in our prayers', 'Expressions of Gratitude in Prayer', 'Both passages emphasize the act of giving thanks to God in prayer for others. The similar phrasing highlights a shared theme of gratitude and intercession in the lives of the authors.', 'theme', 0.37, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 2, 51, 1, 3, 3, 'making mention of you in our prayers', 'Expressions of Gratitude in Prayer', 'Both passages emphasize giving thanks to God and praying for others. This connection highlights a shared theme of gratitude and intercession in the context of prayer.', 'theme', 0.363, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 2, 50, 1, 3, 4, 'making mention of you in our prayers', 'Expressions of Gratitude in Prayer', 'Both passages emphasize giving thanks to God for others in prayer. They highlight the joy and consistency in remembering fellow believers during prayer.', 'theme', 0.356, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 2, 46, 1, 4, 4, 'give thanks to God always', 'Expressions of Gratitude in Prayer', 'Both passages emphasize giving thanks to God always for others, highlighting the importance of prayer in the community. The shared theme of gratitude connects the two letters, reflecting a common practice among early Christians.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 2, 45, 6, 17, 17, 'we give thanks to God', 'Thankfulness for Spiritual Growth', 'This connection highlights the theme of gratitude expressed in both passages. In 1 Thessalonians, Paul gives thanks for the believers, while in Romans, he thanks God for their obedience to doctrine.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 3, 46, 13, 13, 13, 'work of faith, and labour of love', 'Connection of Faith, Hope, and Love', 'Both passages emphasize the importance of faith, hope, and love, highlighting their roles in the Christian life. 1 Thessalonians mentions ''work of faith'' and ''labour of love,'' while 1 Corinthians identifies ''faith, hope, charity'' as essential virtues.', 'theme', 0.482, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 3, 66, 2, 19, 19, 'patience of hope in our Lord Jesus Christ', 'Connection of Works and Patience', 'Both passages emphasize the importance of ''works'' and ''patience'' in the life of believers. They highlight the continuity of faith and love through actions and endurance in Christ.', 'theme', 0.426, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 3, 48, 5, 6, 6, 'work of faith, and labour of love', 'Connection of Faith and Love', 'Both passages emphasize the importance of faith that is active and expressed through love. In 1 Thessalonians, the ''work of faith'' and ''labour of love'' highlight this dynamic, while Galatians points out that faith works through love.', 'theme', 0.398, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 3, 45, 8, 24, 25, 'patience of hope', 'Connection of Hope and Patience', 'Both passages emphasize the importance of hope and patience in the Christian life. In 1 Thessalonians, believers are commended for their ''patience of hope,'' while Romans discusses the necessity of ''patience'' in waiting for unseen hope.', 'theme', 0.37, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 3, 53, 1, 11, 11, 'work of faith', 'Connection of Faith and Work', 'Both passages emphasize the ''work of faith,'' highlighting the importance of faith in the life of believers. The first passage mentions this work in the context of love and hope, while the second passage prays for its fulfillment with power.', 'theme', 0.363, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 3, 62, 5, 3, 3, 'labour of love', 'Connection of Love and Commandments', 'Both passages emphasize the importance of love in the context of faith and obedience. 1 Thessalonians highlights ''labour of love,'' while 1 John connects love to keeping commandments, suggesting that true love manifests in action.', 'theme', 0.356, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 3, 45, 15, 13, 13, 'patience of hope', 'Connection of Hope and Faith', 'Both passages emphasize the theme of hope, with 1 Thessalonians mentioning ''patience of hope'' and Romans highlighting ''God of hope.'' This connection highlights the importance of hope in the believer''s life, supported by faith and the Holy Spirit.', 'theme', 0.349, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 4, 53, 2, 13, 13, 'your election of God', 'Election and Divine Choice', 'Both passages emphasize the concept of being chosen by God. The phrase ''your election of God'' in 1 Thessalonians connects with ''God hath from the beginning chosen you'' in 2 Thessalonians, highlighting the theme of divine selection for salvation.', 'theme', 0.412, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 4, 56, 3, 4, 5, 'your election of God', 'Election and Salvation Connection', 'This connection highlights the theme of God''s election and mercy in salvation. Both passages emphasize God''s initiative in choosing and saving believers, underscoring the transformative work of the Holy Spirit.', 'theme', 0.377, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 4, 61, 1, 10, 10, 'your election of God', 'Connection of Election and Calling', 'Both passages emphasize the concepts of ''election'' and ''calling.'' 1 Thessalonians affirms the believers'' election, while 2 Peter encourages making one''s calling and election sure, suggesting a relationship between the two ideas.', 'theme', 0.377, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 4, 45, 9, 25, 25, 'your election of God', 'Election and Beloved Status', 'This connection highlights the theme of God''s choice in relation to His people. Both passages emphasize the concept of being ''beloved'' and chosen by God, indicating a special status granted to those who were previously not recognized as His people.', 'theme', 0.356, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 4, 51, 3, 12, 12, 'your election of God', 'Election of God Connection', 'Both passages emphasize the concept of being ''elect of God.'' This connection highlights the identity of believers as chosen and beloved, encouraging them to embody virtues such as kindness and humility.', 'theme', 0.349, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 4, 45, 1, 7, 7, 'brethren beloved', 'Beloved of God Connection', 'Both passages emphasize the concept of being ''beloved'' by God. In 1 Thessalonians, the believers are described as ''brethren beloved,'' while Romans addresses those as ''beloved of God.'' This connection highlights the shared identity of the recipients as cherished by God.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 4, 49, 1, 4, 4, 'your election of God', 'Election and Divine Choice', 'Both passages emphasize the concept of being chosen by God. 1 Thessalonians speaks of ''your election of God,'' while Ephesians states ''he hath chosen us in him,'' highlighting the theme of divine selection.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 5, 53, 3, 7, 9, 'what manner of men we were among you', 'Connection of Conduct and Example', 'Both passages emphasize the importance of behavior and example in the Christian community. In 1 Thessalonians, Paul highlights his conduct among them, while in 2 Thessalonians, he urges them to follow his example of hard work and orderliness.', 'theme', 0.384, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 5, 41, 16, 20, 20, 'in power, and in the Holy Ghost', 'Connection of Gospel Power', 'Both passages emphasize the power of the gospel in confirming the message preached. 1 Thessalonians highlights the gospel coming ''in power, and in the Holy Ghost,'' while Mark describes the Lord working with them and confirming the word with signs.', 'theme', 0.377, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 5, 46, 2, 2, 5, NULL, 'Power and the Holy Spirit', 'Both passages emphasize the role of power and the Holy Spirit in preaching. They highlight that true faith is not based on human wisdom but on divine demonstration. This connection underscores the transformative nature of the gospel message.', 'theme', 0.356, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 5, 52, 2, 13, 13, NULL, 'Connection of Word Reception', 'Both passages emphasize the reception of the gospel. The first highlights the power and assurance in the message, while the second stresses that it was received as the word of God, not of men.', 'theme', 0.349, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 5, 60, 1, 12, 12, 'Holy Ghost', 'Connection of the Holy Spirit', 'Both passages emphasize the role of the Holy Ghost in preaching the gospel. They highlight the power and assurance that comes from the Holy Spirit in the ministry of the gospel.', 'theme', 0.349, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 5, 46, 4, 20, 20, 'in word only, but also in power', 'Power in the Gospel Message', 'Both passages emphasize that the gospel is not merely verbal but is demonstrated through power. This connection highlights the transformative impact of the Holy Spirit in the lives of believers.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 5, 48, 3, 2, 5, 'in the Holy Ghost', 'Connection of Spirit and Faith', 'Both passages emphasize the role of the Spirit in the believer''s experience. 1 Thessalonians highlights the power of the Holy Ghost, while Galatians questions whether the Spirit was received through faith or law, linking the two concepts of faith and the Spirit.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 6, 46, 11, 1, 1, 'followers of us, and of the Lord', 'Following Christ and Leaders', 'Both passages emphasize the concept of following leaders who are themselves following Christ. This connection highlights the importance of imitating those who exemplify faith in the Lord.', 'theme', 0.398, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 6, 44, 13, 52, 52, 'joy of the Holy Ghost', 'Joy and the Holy Ghost', 'Both passages emphasize the joy that comes from the Holy Ghost. In 1 Thessalonians, this joy is experienced amidst affliction, while in Acts, it is a characteristic of the disciples.', 'theme', 0.384, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 6, 46, 4, 16, 16, NULL, 'Following the Example of Leaders', 'Both passages emphasize the call to follow leaders in faith. In 1 Thessalonians, the followers are encouraged to imitate both Paul and the Lord, while in 1 Corinthians, Paul directly urges the community to follow him.', 'theme', 0.384, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 6, 48, 5, 22, 22, 'joy of the Holy Ghost', 'Joy of the Holy Ghost', 'Both passages emphasize joy as a key aspect of the Christian experience. In 1 Thessalonians, joy is linked to the Holy Spirit, while Galatians lists joy as a fruit of the Spirit.', 'theme', 0.349, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 6, 53, 3, 9, 9, 'followers of us, and of the Lord', 'Following the Example of Paul', 'Both passages emphasize the idea of following the example set by Paul and the Lord. In 1 Thessalonians, believers are encouraged to become followers, while in 2 Thessalonians, Paul explicitly states he aims to be an example for them to follow.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 6, 49, 5, 1, 1, 'followers of us, and of the Lord', 'Following God and His Messengers', 'Both passages emphasize the concept of following, with 1 Thessalonians encouraging followers of the Lord and Ephesians urging followers of God. This connection highlights the continuity in the call to emulate divine examples.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 6, 64, 1, 11, 11, 'followers of us, and of the Lord', 'Following Good and God', 'This connection highlights the theme of following good examples. Both passages emphasize the importance of following the right path, with 1 Thessalonians encouraging followers of the Lord and 3 John urging to follow what is good.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 7, 56, 2, 7, 7, 'ensamples to all that believe', 'Patterns of Good Works', 'Both passages emphasize the importance of being examples or patterns of good behavior. 1 Thessalonians highlights being ensamples to others, while Titus encourages showing a pattern of good works.', 'theme', 0.419, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 7, 54, 4, 12, 12, 'ensamples to all that believe', 'Examples of Believers', 'Both passages emphasize being an example to others. In 1 Thessalonians, believers are described as ''ensamples,'' while 1 Timothy encourages being ''an example of the believers.'' This connection highlights the importance of modeling faith in various aspects of life.', 'theme', 0.37, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 7, 60, 5, 3, 3, 'ensamples', 'Examples of Faithful Leadership', 'This connection highlights the theme of being ''ensamples'' to others. Both passages emphasize the importance of setting a positive example for believers and the flock.', 'theme', 0.37, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 7, 47, 11, 9, 10, 'Macedonia and Achaia', 'Connection of Macedonian Support', 'Both passages emphasize the role of believers in Macedonia and Achaia. The Thessalonians are described as examples to these regions, while Paul mentions support he received from brethren in Macedonia, highlighting their interconnectedness.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 7, 52, 1, 8, 8, 'ensamples to all that believe', 'Spread of Faith', 'Both passages emphasize the impact of the Thessalonians'' faith as an example to others. The first verse notes they were ''ensamples'' to believers, while the second highlights how their faith ''sounded out'' in various regions.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 7, 44, 16, 12, 12, 'Macedonia and Achaia', 'Macedonia and Achaia Connection', 'Both passages emphasize the significance of Macedonia. 1 Thessalonians mentions believers as examples in Macedonia, while Acts identifies Philippi as a key city in Macedonia.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 7, 44, 1, 13, 13, 'ensamples to all that believe', 'Examples of Believers', 'This connection highlights the idea of being examples to others. In 1 Thessalonians, the believers are described as ''ensamples,'' while Acts lists the apostles who were foundational in the early church.', 'theme', 0.307, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 8, 45, 1, 8, 8, 'your faith to God-ward is spread abroad', 'Faith Spoken of Worldwide', 'Both passages emphasize the widespread reputation of the believers'' faith. In 1 Thessalonians, their faith is ''spread abroad,'' while in Romans, it is ''spoken of throughout the whole world.''', 'theme', 0.37, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 8, 45, 10, 14, 18, 'your faith to God-ward is spread abroad', 'Spread of the Gospel', 'This connection highlights the theme of the spread of faith and the importance of preaching. Both passages emphasize how the message of God reaches far and wide, with the faith of believers resonating in various regions.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 8, 23, 52, 7, 7, NULL, 'Connection of Good Tidings', 'This connection highlights the theme of spreading the word of God. Both passages emphasize the importance of bringing good tidings and proclaiming salvation.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 8, 53, 1, 4, 4, 'your faith to God-ward', 'Faith and Endurance in Persecution', 'Both passages emphasize the believers'' faith and endurance amidst challenges. The faith mentioned in 1 Thessalonians is linked to the patience and faith in 2 Thessalonians, showcasing a consistent theme of steadfastness in trials.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 8, 64, 1, 12, 12, 'your faith to God-ward is spread abroad', 'Faith and Good Report', 'This connection highlights the spread of faith and the commendation of individuals. Both passages emphasize the positive reputation and testimony of believers, showcasing how faith in God is recognized and reported by others.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 8, 66, 14, 6, 6, 'your faith to God-ward is spread abroad', 'Spread of the Gospel', 'This connection highlights the theme of the widespread proclamation of the gospel. Both passages emphasize the dissemination of faith to all nations and peoples.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 8, 53, 3, 1, 1, 'the word of the Lord', 'Connection of Faith and Word', 'Both passages emphasize the spread of ''the word of the Lord'' and the faith of the believers. This connection highlights the importance of faith in facilitating the message of God.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 9, 54, 4, 10, 10, NULL, 'Connection of the Living God', 'Both passages emphasize the concept of the ''living God.'' In 1 Thessalonians, believers turn to serve the ''living and true God,'' while in 1 Timothy, the focus is on trusting in the ''living God.'' This connection highlights the importance of faith in God as a central theme.', 'theme', 0.384, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 9, 46, 12, 2, 2, 'turned to God from idols', 'Idolatry and Turning to God', 'Both passages emphasize the transition from idolatry to serving God. 1 Thessalonians highlights turning to God from idols, while 1 Corinthians mentions being carried away to dumb idols.', 'theme', 0.349, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 9, 48, 4, 8, 9, 'turned to God from idols', 'Turning from Idols to God', 'Both passages emphasize the transition from serving false gods to serving the true God. They highlight the believers'' past idolatry and their current relationship with God, illustrating a significant spiritual transformation.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 9, 36, 2, 11, 11, 'turned to God from idols', 'Turning from Idols to God', 'Both passages emphasize the rejection of idols and the worship of the true God. 1 Thessalonians highlights turning to God from idols, while Zephaniah speaks of the Lord famishing the gods of the earth.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 9, 38, 8, 20, 23, 'turned to God from idols', 'Turning to God and Seeking Him', 'This connection highlights the theme of turning to God and seeking Him. Both passages emphasize a movement towards worshiping the living God and a desire to pray before Him.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 9, 52, 2, 13, 13, 'turned to God from idols', 'Transformation and Reception of God''s Word', 'This connection highlights the theme of turning to God and receiving His word. Both passages emphasize the active response of believers to the truth of God, showcasing a transformation from idols to serving the living God.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 9, 19, 42, 2, 2, NULL, 'Thirst for the Living God', 'This connection highlights the desire for a relationship with the living God. Both passages emphasize turning to God and serving Him, reflecting a deep spiritual longing.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 10, 52, 5, 9, 9, 'wrath to come', 'Connection of Wrath and Salvation', 'Both passages emphasize the theme of deliverance from wrath through Jesus Christ. The first verse mentions being delivered from ''the wrath to come,'' while the second asserts that God has not appointed believers to wrath but to salvation.', 'theme', 0.489, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 10, 23, 25, 8, 9, NULL, 'Connection of Waiting for Salvation', 'Both passages emphasize the theme of waiting for salvation. In 1 Thessalonians, believers wait for Jesus, while Isaiah speaks of waiting for God who will save. This connection highlights the anticipation of divine deliverance.', 'theme', 0.40499999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 10, 45, 5, 9, 10, 'delivered us from the wrath to come', 'Connection of Salvation from Wrath', 'Both passages emphasize salvation from wrath through Jesus. 1 Thessalonians speaks of waiting for Jesus who delivers from wrath, while Romans discusses being saved from wrath through his blood. This connection highlights the theme of deliverance linked to Jesus'' role.', 'theme', 0.384, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 10, 40, 3, 7, 7, 'wrath to come', 'Connection of Wrath to Come', 'Both passages emphasize the concept of ''wrath to come,'' indicating a future judgment. This connection highlights the urgency of repentance and the need for deliverance from impending wrath.', 'theme', 0.377, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 10, 44, 2, 24, 24, 'whom he raised from the dead', 'Resurrection and Deliverance Connection', 'Both passages emphasize the resurrection of Jesus and its significance in delivering believers from death and wrath. 1 Thessalonians highlights waiting for Jesus, while Acts affirms His victory over death.', 'theme', 0.363, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 10, 52, 4, 16, 17, 'wait for his Son from heaven', 'Connection of Christ''s Return', 'Both passages emphasize the return of Jesus from heaven. The first passage mentions waiting for his Son from heaven, while the second describes the Lord descending from heaven.', 'theme', 0.356, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 1, 10, 60, 1, 3, 3, 'whom he raised from the dead', 'Connection of Hope and Resurrection', 'Both passages emphasize the significance of the resurrection of Jesus Christ from the dead. They highlight the hope and deliverance that believers experience through this event, linking the resurrection to salvation from impending wrath.', 'theme', 0.356, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 2, 1, 53, 3, 1, 1, 'not in vain', 'Connection of Prayer and Ministry', 'Both passages emphasize the importance of the word of the Lord. The first verse indicates that their efforts were not in vain, while the second encourages prayer for the word to be glorified, suggesting a continuity in their ministry''s impact.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 2, 1, 19, 127, 1, 1, 'not in vain', 'Vain Labor and Divine Involvement', 'This connection highlights the theme of laboring in vain without divine involvement. Both passages emphasize that efforts are futile unless supported by the Lord''s action.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 2, 1, 35, 2, 13, 13, 'not in vain', 'Connection of Vanity in Labor', 'This connection highlights the theme of vanity in human efforts. Both passages emphasize that labor can be in vain, whether in the context of spiritual ministry or worldly pursuits.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 2, 1, 46, 15, 2, 2, 'in vain', 'Connection of Belief and Purpose', 'This connection highlights the theme of belief not being in vain. Both passages emphasize the importance of genuine faith and the consequences of believing without true conviction.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 2, 1, 46, 15, 58, 58, 'not in vain', 'Connection of Labor and Value', 'Both passages emphasize that labor is not in vain. They highlight the assurance that efforts in faith yield meaningful results. This connection underscores the importance of steadfastness in the work of the Lord.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 2, 1, 50, 2, 16, 16, 'not in vain', 'Connection of Labor and Value', 'Both passages emphasize the idea of labor not being in vain. They reflect a concern for the effectiveness of their efforts in spreading the gospel.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
