(52, 2, 2, 44, 4, 13, 13, 'bold in our God', 'Boldness in Proclaiming the Gospel', 'This connection highlights the theme of boldness in sharing the gospel despite challenges. Both passages emphasize the courage displayed by the apostles in their mission, even when faced with opposition.', 'theme', 0.356, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
