(52, 3, 2, 46, 16, 10, 12, 'minister of God', 'Timothy''s Role in Ministry', 'Both passages emphasize Timothy''s role as a minister and worker in the gospel. In 1 Thessalonians, he is sent to establish and comfort believers, while in 1 Corinthians, Paul encourages the church to receive him without fear, highlighting his importance in ministry.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
