(52, 3, 4, 52, 2, 14, 14, 'suffer tribulation', 'Suffering for Faith Connection', 'Both passages emphasize the theme of suffering for faith. In 1 Thessalonians 3:4, Paul acknowledges the tribulation they would face, while 1 Thessalonians 2:14 highlights the suffering experienced by the Thessalonians, paralleling that of the Judean churches.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(52, 3, 4, 47, 8, 1, 2, 'suffer tribulation', 'Connection of Suffering and Joy', 'Both passages emphasize the experience of suffering and affliction. In 1 Thessalonians, Paul speaks of suffering tribulation, while in 2 Corinthians, the churches of Macedonia endure a great trial of affliction yet respond with joy and generosity.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
